5. e4 $5 ({White can also take the milquetoast route with} 5. Rb1 {, but any red-blooded Veresover would hang his head down in shame if this were played!})
5... Qxb2 6. Nge2 e6 {Choosing to keep the game closed to protect himself from
White's development lead.} ({Instead,} 6... dxe4 $5 7. fxe4 Qa3 8. e5 Nd5 9.
