Nf3 $1 (26. Ndxb5 $6 {allows Black back into the game after} axb5 27. Bxb5 Nxf6
28. Rxe5 Rh4 $1 {and Black is still kicking.}) 26... d4 27. Nxd4 $2 (27. Nxe5
