12. Qe4 $1 {White foresees a superior ending.} exd4 13. Qxe7+ Kxe7 ({
Black can also give up a pawn in the hope of a draw after} 13... Bxe7 14. Nxd4
Nb6 15. Re1 $1 {and after} O-O ({if} 15... Nd5 $2 16. Bc4 Nxe3 17. Rxe3 Kd8 18.
