Rxe2 36. Bxe2 g4 37. Bd3 {and Black can't hold the game. For instance,} Re7 ({
or} 37... a5 38. bxa5 Rxc5 39. Bb5 $1) 38. Rxe7 Kxe7 39. Be4 {.}) 32. Bxa6 bxc5
