Rg6 22. Bd3 Rg7 23. Qe1 O-O {Giving up on his dreams.} ({
If he continues to attack with} 23... f5 {then} 24. Ng2 h5 25. Kf1 Bb7 26. Qe3
{shuts Black down.}) 24. Nc4 f5 25. Qe5 $1 {Following three principles. When
