h7 Kg7 36. Nxf6 {This must have been annoying for Akobian. White's knight is a
multi-tasker who has regained the sac'ed pawn, is untouchable on f6 and
secures the h-pawn.} Nf5 $1 {Akobian puts up maximum resistance. His plan: ...Nh6 and ...Nf7, which covers the queening square and wins the lead h-pawn.
