13. Nc4 Qc7 14. Ne5 Rad8 15. Rad1 {
(I expected Tigarano to go ballistic and sac on h7)} Bf8 16. c4 Nxe5 $5 17.
dxe5 Nd7 18. Bxh7+ $5 {(there we go!)} Kxh7 19. Qxf7 Re7 20. Qh5+ Kg8 21. Rd3
g6 $1 ({throughout my life, I have always been an incompetent attacker and an
