time scrambles.}) 9... O-O $5 {I decided to allow him his 'threat' Na5.} 10.
Na5 {Jack was under the impression that my last move was a blunder.} ({Instead,
} 10. Re1 b6 11. Nce5 Nxe5 12. dxe5 Nd7 (12... Ne4 $5 {is a possibility}) 13.
