} 26... Ng5 $1 27. Be2 ({the immediate lunge doesn't quite do it after} 27. Qa6
$2 Nxf3 28. Bb5 Nxd4 29. Bxd7 Qxe4 30. Rc1 Rcd8) 27... h5 $1 {.}) 27. Qc3 {
